onessh (0.4.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add environment variable ONESSH_IMPORT_KEYFILE in configuration time to
    set ONESSH_ALLOWED_USERS automatically and copy the keyfile instead of
    importing keys for each user via "ssh-import-id".

